<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="F" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Famish" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Famish,</orth> 1) tr. to starve, to distress with hunger: <bibl n="shak. ven 20" default="NO" valid="yes">Ven. 20</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mv 2.2.113" default="NO" valid="yes">Merch. II, 2, 113</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. shr 4.3.3" default="NO" valid="yes">Shr. IV, 3, 3</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h4 5.4.22" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B V, 4, 22</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h5 3.5.57" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 III, 5, 57</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 1.2.7" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A I, 2, 7</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 1.4.68" default="NO" valid="yes">I, 4, 68</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h6 1.3.175" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B I, 3, 175</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h6 4.10.47" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 10, 47</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 5.3.329" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 V, 3, 329</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tit 5.3.179" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. V, 3, 179</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tim 4.3.535" default="NO" valid="yes">Tim. IV, 3, 535</bibl>. <cit><quote>a single --ed kiss,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tro 4.4.49" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. IV, 4, 49</bibl></cit> (i. e. hungry, longing for more). <cit><quote>mine eye is --ed for a look,</quote> <bibl n="shak. son 47.3" default="NO" valid="yes">Sonn. 47, 3</bibl></cit>.<lb />2) intr. to die of hunger: <bibl n="shak. 2h6 4.10.2" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B IV, 10, 2</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 3h6 5.4.32" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C V, 4, 32</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cor 1.1.5" default="NO" valid="yes">Cor. I, 1, 5</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cor 1.1.5" default="NO" valid="yes">Cor. I, 1, 5</bibl> <bibl n="shak. tit 2.3.154" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. II, 3, 154</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. per 1.4.12" default="NO" valid="yes">Per. I, 4, 12</bibl>. With an accus. denoting the result: <cit><quote>thou shalt f. a dog's death,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tim 2.2.91" default="NO" valid="yes">Tim. II, 2, 91</bibl></cit> (some M. Edd. <emph>f., a dog's death).</emph>
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>